<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="4Oct1933"><font color="red">4 October 1933</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from F.V. Morely to JJ): There is a thing called the Sunday Times Book Exhibition &hellip; (Sutherland House, Mayfair) from Nov 6th - Nov 20th and in connection with the exhibition there is to be a Loan Collection of manuscripts and incunabula. The Loan Collection is whirmering for a manuscript of yours; and I want to know if I could have your permission to lend them pages 28 and 29 [BL Add. MS 47475 fols. 105v, 106r, from <a name="bd8y" href="../../ff/fdra/bda.htm#bd8y">I.2&sect;2.8+</a>] of the corrected text of WORK IN PROGRESS? These are pages of &ldquo;transition&rdquo; with interesting corrections and additions. </div>
